1. *Rene* je bio veoma zauzet u poslednje vreme. (Rene has been very busy lately.)
2. Izabrali smo *renu* kao dodatak jelu. (We chose horseradish as an addition to the dish.)
3. Srećom, *ren* je pomogao da ublažim prehladu. (Luckily, horseradish helped me relieve my cold.)
4. Ukoliko ne volite *ren*, možete ga zameniti nekim drugim začinom. (If you don't like horseradish, you can replace it with some other spice.)
5. Nakon što sam pojela *ren*, osetila sam kako mi gori jezik. (After I ate horseradish, I felt my tongue burning.)
6. Da li si probao *renovu* čorbu? (Have you tried horseradish soup?)
7. *Reneova* sestra je vrlo talentovana muzičarka. (Rene's sister is a very talented musician.)
8. U polju se nalazi *renje*, koji se koristi kao lekovita biljka. (In the field, there is horseradish, which is used as a medicinal plant.)
9. Da li znaš gde mogu da kupim *rene*? (Do you know where I can buy horseradish?)
10. Preporučujem ti da probaš jelo sa malo *rena* - sjajan je dodatak ukusu! (I recommend you to try a dish with a little bit of horseradish - it's a great addition to the taste!)